  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://www.inf.ufrgs.br/ontologies/copi/COPI_0000026">
    <iof-av:naturalLanguageDefinition xml:lang="en">A DesignedFunction that is realized in a FlowControlProcess and that consists in the capacity to permit, obstruct, divert or regulate the flow of fluids through a conduit or system by means of mechanical positioning within the flow stream.</iof-av:naturalLanguageDefinition>
    <iof-av:naturalLanguageDefinition xml:lang="en">A DesignedFunction that is realized in a FlowControlProcess and that consists in the capacity to regulate, direct, or restrict the flow of fluids through a system by means of movable internal components.</iof-av:naturalLanguageDefinition>
    <iof-av:naturalLanguageDefinition xml:lang="en">A DesignedFunction that is realized in a FlowControlProcess and that consists in the capacity to regulate, direct, or interrupt the flow of fluids through a conduit or system by means of movable elements that alter flow passages.</iof-av:naturalLanguageDefinition>
    <rdfs:subClassOf rdf:nodeID="n23a17477f6ab465c9b392a22c900a573b171"/>
